    "After the third phase, we identified 41 primary studies directly relevant to our research focus.",
    "The search process is conducted on November 14th, 2024.The paper must be written in English.",
    "The paper must have an accessible full text.",
    "The paper must adopt LMA techniques to solve software engineering-related tasks.",
    "The paper has less than 5 pages."
